<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Ocean City Rentals</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Welcome to Ocean City Rentals, your premier source for vacation rental properties
          in Ocean City, New Jersey.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Bob Idell Real Estate</h2>
        <p>
          Bob Idell Real Estate has been serving the Ocean City community for years,
          helping families find their perfect vacation rental. We understand that your
          beach vacation is important, and we're committed to making the rental process
          as smooth as possible.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Why Ocean City, NJ?</h2>
        <p>
          Ocean City is America's Greatest Family Resort. With miles of beautiful beaches,
          a vibrant boardwalk, and countless family-friendly activities, it's the perfect
          destination for your summer vacation.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 space-y-2">
          <li>8 miles of pristine beaches</li>
          <li>2.5 mile boardwalk with shops and attractions</li>
          <li>Family-friendly atmosphere (dry town)</li>
          <li>Water sports, fishing, and boating</li>
          <li>Annual events and festivals</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Browse Our Properties</h2>
        <p>
          We have <%= number_with_delimiter(Property.count) %> properties available for
          vacation rental in Ocean City. Use our search feature to find the perfect
          property for your family vacation.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <%= link_to "Browse All Properties", properties_path,
            class: "inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 font-semibold" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
